LEGIONELLOSIS, HISTORICAL DATA - USA
************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
See Also
Legionellosis - USA (Pennsylvania) 980715224022
Date: Fri, 17 Jul 1998 09:51:50 +0000
From: Steve Berger <mberger@post.tau.ac.il>

The following historical data on legionellosis for the USA were extracted
from the GIDEON software program. Note that the true incidence is
estimated at 10,000 to 15,000 per year.
Year Number
1976 to 1985 5,917
1986 948
1987 1,038
1988 1,085
1989 1,190
1990 1,370
1991 1,317
1992 1,339
1993 1,241
1994 1,615
1995 1,241
1996 1,198
1997 1,054 (preliminary)
--
Dr. Steve Berger
e-mail: mberger@post.tau.ac.il
[In response to my inquiry, Steve has indicated that these data are derived
from CDC records for all 50 states. - Mod.ES
